<template>
  <router-view />
</template>

<script>
import axios from "axios";

export default {
  name: "App",
  data() {
    return {
      info: null,
    };
  },
  mounted() {
    axios
      .get("https://apic.polytech.kz/api/v1/concerts")
      .then((response) => (this.info = response));
  },
};
</script>

<style></style>
